column1: #Text=As the report only includes figures from crimes reported to law enforcement , it is likely that real crime numbers were higher .
#Text=We 're seeing more schemes involving bigger ticket items , get-rich-quick and work-at-home schemes that involve higher dollar losses .

#Text=FBI Cyber Division Assistant Director James E. Finch commented on the report : " The Internet presents a wealth of opportunity for would be criminals to prey on unsuspecting victims , and this report shows how extensive these types of crime have become ... What this report does not show is how often this type of activity goes unreported .
